{"word":"μεσοπαγής","slug":"μεσοπαγής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n66472\" key=\"mesopagh/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μεσο-πᾰγής</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"pref\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μεσσο-</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">παγῆναι</etym>) <sense id=\"n66472.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fixed up to the middle</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μεσσοπαγὲς δ᾽ ἄρ᾽ ἔθηκε κατ᾽ ὄχθης μείλινον ἔγχος</foreign> drove it in <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">up to the middle</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:172\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.172</biblScope> </bibl>:—<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> preferred the <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l.</abbr> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μεσσοπαλές</orth>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">quivering up to the middle</tr_> (cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>); but it is doubtful whether -<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παλές</foreign> could mean <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">quivering</tr_>, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μεσσοπαγής</foreign> is found in late Poets, as <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:233\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.233</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}